title.narrative: Effective & Efficient management of the Health & Nutrition programme

description.narrative: UNICEF Lao PDR efficiently mobilized the technical expertise required to provide strategic and technical guidance and support to MoH and partners in planning, implementing and monitoring the country’s comprehensive health and nutrition programme. Facing the global pandemic, additional technical expertise, guidance and resources were provided, enabling an efficient response to the emergency. As a result, UNICEF significantly contributed to the containment of the COVID-19 outbreak and prevented a deterioration of essential child and maternal health and nutrition services. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/01/2022
